### Expected Performance Gains

| Optimization | Time Saved | Cost Reduction | Success Rate |
|--------------|------------|----------------|--------------|
| Confirmed Commitment | 50-100ms | - | - |
| Skip Preflight | ~100ms | - | - |
| Priority Fees | - | Varies | +5-10% |
| CU Optimization | - | 10-30% | +2-5% |
